    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a reliable and well-cared-for machine. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic paint that retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front fascia and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. All body panels are original and properly aligned. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the leather upholstery shows a light, natural patina on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but remains free of any tears or punctures. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent oil service and brake inspection completed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. It has been garaged throughout its life and comes with a complete set of service records, two keys, and original floor mats. This is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for its next chapter.",
